OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fbright through this evening before
OL,7,Fpatchy low cloud moves in from the
OL,8,Feast leaving a few clear spells.
OL,9,FTemperatures will fall away to low
OL,10,Fsingle figures with a couple frosty
OL,11,Fpatches, most likely in sheltered
OL,12,Frural areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FAfter early morning cloud
OL,15,Fclears, another bright and sunny day
OL,16,Fwill follow for all. Winds lighter
OL,17,Fthan Wednesday allowing temperatures
OL,18,Fto climb further. UV levels will also
OL,19,Fbe high.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
